title: SebP
author: SebP
content: Attention Entrepreneurs and Business Owners! Are you looking to bring your startup idea to life and handle everything in between? Look no further!I'm looking for long-term partners rather than just "clients". I'm interested in serious entrepreneurs with innovative ideas. If you're just looking for someone cheap to do the coding then I don't think we are right fit for each other.I'm really good and experienced at what I do thus I require good recompensation.I've built multiple projects from scratch, been a team member of companies like Stripe, I have a good network of devs and designers if you want to scale in the future. I can plan out your project based on your requirements, connect you and push you in the right direction. I know the startup/crypto world through, with my 10y of expertise in the latest technologies and frameworks I can help turn your vision into a reality.I get paid in stables.For more information about me, the technologies I use, or anything else; please send me a DM here, and I will contact you ASAP.PS: DM me your fav book or talk about something you're interested in.
